<paragraph blockId="83.[2088,2674,591,1018]" pageId="83" pageNumber="698">Although “Hirola” is the spelling of the common name most often used today, Sclater in 1889 originally spelled it “Herola” after the Oromo name. Monotypic.</paragraph>
